<HEADLINE>
<P>
IT DEPENDS ON WHO'S DOING THE LOOKING 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 "Night Crawlers" should give America a good look at what is wrong with its 
youth today (Fashion, May 1). If looks mean anything, we are in big trouble. 
</P>
<P>
 CHUCK WILSON 
</P>
<P>
 Yorba Linda 
</P>
</TEXT>
