<HEADLINE>
<P>
NEWS, TIPS & BARGAINS; CAR RENTALS FOR FREE SPIRITS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Many savvy travelers bound for foreign shores line up their rental cars before 
they leave home, a tactic that usually results in considerable savings but 
requires some planning ahead. 
</P>
<P>
 Now Kemwel, a company based in Harrison, N.Y., that offers international car 
rentals and European car leases among other travel services, has a service for 
the free spirits among us. 
</P>
<P>
 Kemwel's new CarPass Plan enables travelers to prepay for their car rentals in 
U.S. dollars but choose their rental dates after they arrive at their 
destinations. This provides the flexibility of renting on the spot while saving 
20% to 50% off local rates. 
</P>
<P>
 Each CarPass is valid for three consecutive days in six countries. Unused 
passes are fully refundable upon return to the United States. Travelers may buy 
as many passes as they want. They may be redeemed through March 31, 1995, based 
on availability. For information, call Kemwel at (800) 678-0678. 
</P>
