 Security sources said the South Lebanon Army, Israel's surrogate militia, 
detected the infiltrators and fired shells from tanks, killing the three men. 
</P>
<P>
 Hezbollah, or the Party of God, is fighting to force Israel out of its 
self-declared security zone in Lebanon. 
