<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA060594-0315 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 048664 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
June 5, 1994, Sunday, Valley Edition 
</P>
